data.title: Mon sang dans tes veines. Roman aprés une idée de Joséphine Baker by (BAKER, Josephine). Félix Achille de la Cámara; Pepito Abatino: Very Good Softcover (1931) Signed by Author(s)
data.meta_description: Signed by Author(s) - 1st Edition - Softcover - Les editions Isis, Paris - 1931 - Condition: Very Good - First edition. Octavo. 178, [4]pp. Illustrations de G. de Pogédaïeff. Illustrated paper wrappers. Page edges toned, small chips and tears along the spine, a near very good copy. A novel based on an idea by Josephine Baker. Warmly Inscribed by la Camera, Abatino, and by Josephine Baker. - Mon sang dans tes veines. Roman aprés une idée de Joséphine Baker
